<subSubSection id="C34F6577FFFDFFAEFF2462F893B69991" pageId="15" pageNumber="45" type="diagnosis">
<paragraph id="8BEA36FCFFFDFFAEFF2462F893B69991" blockId="15.[151,1436,510,751]" pageId="15" pageNumber="45">
<emphasis id="B921EAEEFFFDFFAEFF2462F8913699FC" bold="true" box="[201,323,654,679]" pageId="15" pageNumber="45">Diagnosis.</emphasis>
Shell fragile, posterodorsal area with a siphonal gap and defined by a line from umbones to posterior end; hinge with conspicuous cardinal teeth and rudimentary laterals.
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
